title: Emma Boster from Dying Wish
itunes:title: Emma Boster from Dying Wish
description:
Boy oh boy do I love Dying Wish and in turn, I had to have Emma Boster the vocalist of said band on the pod ASAP. We accomplished that and discussed how sick Portland is, the art of booking shows and how important MySpace-core was for music tastes of the early 2000's. Emma was a great hang and enjoy our discussion! 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
